3. **Configure Conditions**:
   - Set thresholds (e.g., > 100 errors/hour)
   - Filter by tags, environment, or release
   - Set time windows (5min, 15min, 1hour, etc.)

4. **Set Actions**:
   - Email notification
   - Slack notification
   - PagerDuty integration
   - Custom webhooks

5. **Save and Test**:
