### GET /api/jobs/:jobId

Get details for a single job.

**Response:**
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "id": "duplicate-detection-1705312200000",
    "pipelineId": "duplicate-detection",
    "status": "completed",
    "createdAt": "2024-01-15T10:00:00.000Z",
    "startedAt": "2024-01-15T10:00:01.000Z",
